OL,3,CThousands sign petition calling for
OL,4,C'Spudman's' pitch to be reinstated
OL,6,FA potato seller who has been moved off
OL,7,Fhis town centre pitch in order for a
OL,8,Fflowerbed to be created said he is
OL,9,F"destroyed by the news".
OL,11,FBen Newman, also known as Spudman, had
OL,12,Fbeen told last year that he would be
OL,13,Ftemporarily moved from his spot but
OL,14,Fwill now be moved permanently.
OL,16,FHe has traded in St Editha's Square in
OL,17,FTamworth for 22 years but Tamworth
OL,18,FCouncil say they need the pitch back
OL,19,Fbecause they say they need the space
OL,20,Fto do regeneration work in the area.
