OL,3,CThousands sign petition calling for
OL,4,C'Spudman's' pitch to be reinstated
OL,6,FHe has been offered a new pitch by the
OL,7,Fcouncil but says it will be bad for
OL,8,Fhis business and will block views of
OL,9,Fthe church.
OL,11,FBen bought the pitch for #100,000 and
OL,12,Fhas been selling potatoes from his van
OL,13,Fsince 2003.
OL,15,FSpudman says his original site is the
OL,16,Fonly suitable location for the
OL,17,Fshipping container which he already
OL,18,Fordered, which he planned to use as
OL,19,Fhis business expands.
