OL,4,C'Spudman's' pitch to be reinstated
OL,6,FHe has strongly established himself in
OL,7,Fthe community since, amassing four
OL,8,Fmillion followers on TikTok and over a
OL,9,Fmillion followers on facebook.
OL,11,FHe's also raised thousands of pounds
OL,12,Ffor kidney charities, a cause close to
OL,13,Fhis heart due to his own health issues.
OL,15,FSpudman posted a video online saying
OL,16,F"I have lost my pitch to a flowerbed"
OL,17,Fand that he doesn't want to move
OL,18,Fbecause "that's where I built my
OL,19,Fbusiness, that's where everyone knows
OL,20,FI am".
